{"tid":1671700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔想去加泰集會/覺得Ventus係鬼既同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-23T15:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T23:56:09.000Z","uid":248120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"920b87fffd5aa5e196006f86b50341e54ba61ea2","tid":1671700,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"唔想傷害「西班牙人民感情」⋯⋯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">咪黎10.26愛丁堡反DQ晚宴囉！</span></strong></span><br />\n順便見埋啱先被人DQ完既黃敎主都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道「嬲一日」係香港民族既劣根性<br />\n我知道「要返工不了」係香港民族既欽定辯解<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係你唔好將天公地道既公民權、參政權都當成係一種恩賜先得架！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n26號晚<br />\n我要大家一齊帶碟糖醋肉入黎<br />\n酒性好既就帶埋Chivas Regal 12黎<br />\n因爲呢D都係朴正熙今生人最後既飯餸<br />\n呢D都係佢以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>政變、修憲、DQ</strong></span>所爭取返黎既！<br />\n<br />\n當年金載圭個兩槍<br />\n幫成個釜山擋住佢地十幾萬槍<br />\n避免進一步既屠城<br />\n我地點可以就咁過橋抽板架？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkbip55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwkbip55.jpg&h=8314cf96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2O1voe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2O1voe.jpg&h=6e230693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b38a1a89a75534d20cd743c3d23b8fe02d7e71cf","tid":1671700,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"882c8ef7356826ce072fa1b4ae51be9900ba20d3","tid":1671700,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38a1a89a75534d20cd743c3d23b8fe02d7e71cf","tid":1671700,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"Good<br />\n推爆佢<br />\